  ReadData of Port Interface DidServices_ID_MeasValue_2431

    


    

    
448

    
    

    
    ReadData allows requesting to the application the data value of a DID. If the length of the DID is variable, the operation ReadDataLength has to provide the currently valid data length of this DID.

    


    

    
449

    
    

    
     The operation is used for the UDS Service ReadDataByIdentifier and for the UDS Service ReadDataByPeriodicIdentifier (0x2A).

    


    

    
450

    
    

    

    


    

    
451

    
    

    
     The ReadData operation is present if the DcmDspDidInfo container that is referenced by DcmDspDid/DcmDspDidInfoRef contains the element DcmDspAccess/DcmDspDidRead.

    ReadData allows requesting to the application the data value of a DID. If the length of the DID is variable, the operation ReadDataLength has to provide the currently valid data length of this DID.

    


    

    
658

    
    

    
     The operation is used for the UDS Service ReadDataByIdentifier and for the UDS Service ReadDataByPeriodicIdentifier (0x2A).

    


    

    
659

    
    

    

    


    

    
660

    
    

    
     The ReadData operation is present if the DcmDspDidInfo container that is referenced by DcmDspDid/DcmDspDidInfoRef contains the element DcmDspAccess/DcmDspDidRead.

    


    

    
661

    
    

    

    


    

    
662
